0-22T15:40:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好簡單<br />\n<br />\n用價錢分辦，唔洗咁多廢話的</blockquote><br />\n有錢就唔洗問啦，就係無先問點分真假4k"},{"pid":"b712518b157ec2ed272dd870bcf4bad628d5b58a","tid":444432,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T15:42:51.000Z","msg":"$4500<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97a4542b417327e8f3497c859d63ffc13ca2bb1a","tid":444432,"uid":79829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T16:26:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咩係假4k?</blockquote><br />\nrgbw</blockquote><br />\n有無例子睇睇"},{"pid":"38a4c7629bd8ae8079daed0162bb7560d120711e","tid":444432,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T17:08:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咩係假4k?</blockquote><br />\nrgbw</blockquote><br />\n有無例子睇睇</blockquote><br />\n想買lg 49UH6500電視,但啲人話係假4k!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/282735/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/282735/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n假4k畫質仲差過full hd，否則我一早買咗"},{"pid":"0c13670958742e6432c1b09f37acc65717490ad8","tid":444432,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T17:20:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咩係假4k?</blockquote><br />\nrgbw</blockquote><br />\n有無例子睇睇</blockquote><br />\n大陸新推出低價4K電視 其實都是假4K大陸新推出低價4K電視 其實都是假4K<br />\nBack選單留名<br />\n<br />\n你識乜春 1255日<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.3dmgame.com/hardware/201405/3276827.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.3dmgame.com%2Fhardware%2F201405%2F3276827.html&d=ytPBNWVX11MqgvXu93vcRTOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=f7b12e21\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.3dmgame.com/hardware/201405/3276827.html</a><br />\n國內的4K電視層出不窮，而且價格看上去似乎非常吸引人，實際上呢?首先來看幾個關鍵詞，49寸LG/華星光電面板，這個尺寸的面板，還是lg/華星光電。大家都知道， 華星光電是三星乾兒子（早在2011年就有參股投資關係），三星能做假4k，華星光電自然也可以。目前來說， 49寸這個尺寸的面板有三種規格: <br />\n<br />\n第一種 RGB 1080p， <br />\n<br />\n第二種RGBW +Half Cut 1080p（可以用來做假4k） <br />\n<br />\n第三種 RGB 4K。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n目前來說, 存在一個比較無恥的現象， 那就是很多國產廠家， 把那個RGBW + 半像素的1080p， 當做4k來賣。這是因為， 我國的4k標準有漏洞，只標明了分辨率3840x2160，是什麼分辨率，卻沒說。 <br />\n<br />\n那個&ldquo;假4K&rdquo;面板， 他的實際物理分辨率是7680x2160;但是問題在於， 這是半像素技術面板， 不是兩個像素， 所以實際上真正有效的物理像素只有7680x1080。它為什麼說是4k呢? 因為這裡借鑒了YUV視頻規範的說法。這是最無恥的一點。 RGB三色像素，合成一個亮度通道像素，W，本身就是一個亮度通道像素,這種面板， 他的理論亮度通道分辨率是3840x1080，當然按照國內的半像素也是像素的謬論，就是3840x2160的亮度通道分辨率。完全符合我國所謂的4K標準/規範。 <br />\n<br />\n這種所謂的&ldquo;4k&rdquo;，在日本是不能叫做&ldquo;4k&rdquo;的，它還是1080p面板，因為日本規範是彩色完全分辨率達到3840x2160以上。而中國祇寫了分辨率3840x2160, 大有空子可鑽。這種假&ldquo;假4K&rdquo;，按照物理分辨率來計算，其實是RGB1080p面板的精細版，當然，從性能上，也是改良版。 <br />\n<br />\n暗示 大米嗎"},{"pid":"7e4c5d5704172aaebd25e6a64b8d2845619a20f6","tid":444432,"uid":79829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T17:24:49.000Z","msg":"呢隻真定假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.lg.com/hk/monitor/lg-24UD58-B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lg.com%2Fhk%2Fmonitor%2Flg-24UD58-B&d=ytPBNWVX11MqgvXu93vcRTOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=1efb3e17\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.lg.com/hk/monitor/lg-24UD58-B</a>"},{"pid":"f917b9b5c5350690eb170cb7a0c80e96a07e2228","tid":444432,"uid":139538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T19:02:19.000Z","msg":"假4k像素2880"},{"pid":"fff4cfda6e31b00a3f30ff883a2a30dbda486739","tid":444432,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T01:13:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af03aa390b8834a50689f49b8c4805decd18f496","tid":444432,"uid":35408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T01:14:57.000Z","msg":"有貴買貴囉<br />\n冇錢學咩人玩4k<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69a7966640b92bba56b8eb3063c5e9f1f62d107c"